    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343370/extras/d4f4fc68ce1795dbb668c207e252927d.poster.avif?t=1758386727\" width=512 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343370/extras/d4f4fc68ce1795dbb668c207e252927d.webm?t=1758386727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Last Root </strong> follows a young cactus on a quest to save her family and world from the hold of an evil dictator. Join her as she gains friends, defeats enemies in party-based combat, explores her diverse world -  and maybe even saves the day. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343370/extras/7b92e60779e8450c4ebd9e417aca808a.apng?t=1758386727\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343370/extras/7b92e60779e8450c4ebd9e417aca808a.poster.avif?t=1758386727\" class=\"bb_img\" width=528 height=192 /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A robust cast of lovable (and hateable) characters from aloe to ZZ<br></li><li> Complex villains who are more than simply villainous <br></li><li> An immersive pixel-art world with a variety of cultures and terrain <br></li><li> A morality system that will determine your fate<br></li><li> Find and grow your own seedlings; a unique and customizable class of fighters <br></li><li> Help your teammates in battle with interactive assist minigames <br></li><li> Plants, of course! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343370/extras/651a2c6360031c087278fbb5135290a7.apng?t=1758386727\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343370/extras/651a2c6360031c087278fbb51